dmca.title: Spanish Company Complains of Defamatory and Offensive Postings
dmca.body:
We request the suppression of the specified URL because we have found some offending pages with our Google search results about our company. We have found it on Google's search "revelance SA":
1.	The Google website where the information above appears: Google.es, Piginas en espafiol
2.	Identify our country of residence and citizenship: Espana
3.	Identify precisely the information that you claim violates your rights under applicable law (the "Unlawful Material"). Some information contained in the forums:

[redacted]
